<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.7">
<l>pēcavun tariyāta peṇmaiyiṉ pētaiyēṉ pētaiyivaḷ</l>
<l>kūcamiṉṟi niṉṟārkaḷ tammetir kōlkaḻintāṉ mūḻaiyāy</l>
<l>kēcavāveṉ ṟuṅkēṭi līyeṉṟuṅ kiñcuka vāymoḻiyāḷ</l>
<l>vācavār kuḻalmaṅkai mīrivaḷ māluṟu kiṉṟāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She is the foolish, simple girl of me, a simple woman,</l>
<l rend="indent">who, even if I [want to] speak, I cannot.</l>
<l>Like a ladle that has slipped from [its] handle,</l>
<l rend="indent">she sounds like a parrot</l>
<l>saying “Keśava” and “Imperishable One”</l>
<l rend="indent">in front of those who remain without shame.</l>
<l>Ladies with long, fragrant tresses! She has gone mad!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
